Summary: Ability to do NTLM authentication in various contexts (eg. proxy)
Class: wish
Difficulty: taxing
Priority: low
Content-type: text/x-html-body

<p>
Occasionally people ask for support for NTLM authentication in various
contexts (e.g. for HTTP proxy authentication).

<p>
NTLM authentication appears to be proprietary to Microsoft; what
<a href="http://www.innovation.ch/java/ntlm.html">public documentation</a>
there is appears to be reverse engineered.
